headline: Applied Data Finance Strengthens Executive Team with Key Leadership Appointments to Accelerate AI-Driven Lending
summary: SAN DIEGO, July 31, 2025--Applied Data Finance (ADF), a fintech innovator dedicated to expanding fair and responsible credit access for underestimated U.S. consumers through AI-powered underwriting, today announced appointments to its executive and leadership teams, further solidifying its commitment to providing scalable, transparent, and data-driven lending solutions.
